external_knowledge:
; A "cited publication" refers to a publication that has been referenced or cited by other publications; 
; The citations are counted to determine the popularity or impact of a publication; 
; The "top 10 most cited publications" refers to the publications with the highest citation counts; 
; The "authors" and "research areas" of a publication refer to the individuals who wrote the publication and the fields of study related to the publication, respectively.
